{"tid":2215950,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不和美國同陣線！傳默克爾反對禁止華為5G","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T06:16:29.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ff245e2d382313412862f6cff20d18ec29a467ed","tid":2215950,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:27:48.000Z","msg":"外界在美中貿易、科技戰中，於歐洲方面一直關注德國態度，而隨著德國已制定5G無線網路安全規則草案，該國也傳出其總理梅克爾（Angela Merkel）正在抵抗國內鷹派，以避免德國正式禁止中國華為公司，參與該國的5G網路建設。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》今（23）報導，3名知情人士透露，德國已制定5G無線網路安全規則草案，其將加強政府對設備供應商的審查，讓德國主要內閣成員有更多空間，指出德國的數據安全風險。而核心立場為德國絕不能針對性禁止華為的德國總理梅克爾，則拒絕就其立場做出妥協。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士指出，德國的5G無線網路安全規則仍會改變，但該規則無意透過嚴格的安全要求，而在實際上成為華為禁令，德國的規則也不會讓電信公司在使用華為產品的作業上，變得過於繁瑣或風險變高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3301290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3301290&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=86b3aa84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3301290&h=61829269\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3301290</a><br />\n<br />\n彭博：<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-22/merkel-resists-full-ban-on-huawei-making-germany-an-outlier\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2020-09-22%2Fmerkel-resists-full-ban-on-huawei-making-germany-an-outlier&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=bdd25541\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-22/merkel-resists-full-ban-on-huawei-making-germany-an-outlier</a>"},{"pid":"f932f51ac3f06c2337301352f022ee99fa144a28","tid":2215950,"uid":155095,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgOwF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgOwF4.jpg&h=9d2ee8d2&s={SIZE}\" />"}